Bundled language data — Universal Dependencies
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The `lemmas:` and `verbs:` data (and part of `function_words:`) in the files
under `worddata/` are derived from the Universal Dependencies (UD) treebanks,
https://universaldependencies.org/.

This data is provided under the licenses of the respective UD treebanks
(predominantly CC BY-SA or CC BY), NOT under the Caveman software license.
See LICENSE, Section 2.

Please cite Universal Dependencies:

  Marie-Catherine de Marneffe, Christopher D. Manning, Joakim Nivre,
  Daniel Zeman. "Universal Dependencies." Computational Linguistics (2021).

